Struct aero_kernel::fs::cache::Cache

source · [−]
pub struct Cache<K: CacheKey, V: Cacheable<K>> {
    index: Mutex<CacheIndex<K, V>>,
    self_ref: Weak<Cache<K, V>>,
}
Expand description

Structure representing a cache with a key of K and value of V. The cache key is used to get the cache from the cache index. This structure basically contains the cache index (protected by a mutex) and a weak self reference to itself.
